my sister is breaking up with her boyfriend so she's all pissy and bitchy and grr, i feel icky... we found a frog in the yard today, we brought it in and were playing with it, then we let it go in the forest, it probably hopped off to find some swamp weed and went on the trip of a lifetime: he met a rainbow boa constricter that was winding itself up a pink elephant's trunk, he followed them them into a cave where a siamese komodo dragon was blowing naked woman shaped bubbles, which he would then attack and eat, until one of the bubbles turned out being a lesbian and she ran off with another one of the bubble girls, so the frog decided to follow them into their lair where he found them having an orgy with the boa and some other bubble girls they had found on the way, the frog joined in for a while but one by one the bubble girls popped, and finally he was alone with the boa so he decided to sneak away before the snake realized the crevice he was in was only a hole in the rocks, the frog stumbled out and fell down a hole where he met a one-eyed bunny named frank, frank introduced him to a rabid penguin before hopping off and stalking some schitzo kid, the frog and the penguin went off together to hook up with the penguin's roommate who had a bong and some british little kid program movies, so they went off in search of the penguin's roommate, but on the way the frog got knocked out by a giant raisin that fell on his head, when he woke up he saw shadowy figures looming above him, each of them holding some reflective pointy thing, they brought the shiny-ness down and into his stomach, making incisions and cuts and taking things out, the frog was still dissoriented so he didn't complain, until one of the figures started ripping his muscles off of his bones, he tried to get up but he couldn't, finally he worked up the energy to twitch his foot, but it was too late, he was only a skeleton below his non-existent neck, only his head and feet were left intact, when he twitched the giant let go of him with a shriek, and he was dropped on his back.  He wiggled around and pushed himself onto his back, then proceeded to the nearest opening.  he stepped out the door but instead of entering a hallway he found himself in a circus ring with clowns and cannabalistic muffins running around on dying fish, he tried to go back the way he came from but he then realized the ring was on a tiny platform hanging in the middle of an active volcano, he tried to hide but then a clown picked him up by his tongue and started twirling him around, when the clown stopped he had turned into a bundle of ribbons and couldn't move himself, the clown then stuck him up his nose and pulled him out of his ass, when he came out he had been transformed into a japanese dung beetle, in this form he managed to crawl away undetected past the muffins who were eating each other (in more than one way), he then burrowed himself under the sawdust and kept digging until he reached  water.  He opened his eyes (they had been closed to keep the dirt out) and he was sitting on an island inhabited by millions of johnny depps (not johnny depp look alikes, but actual johnny depps), and they were all around playing guitar and drawing and writing, and in the middle of an island there was a tent set up with a girl named diana, and all of the johnny depps were waiting to have their turn fucking her and singing to her and talking to her and drawing for her and just having a wonderful time in general with her, anyway back to the frog that was now a dung beetle, one of the johnny depps decided he would make a cool earring for diana so he tried to poke a hole through him but as soon as the needle hit his side he transformed into a dolphin and knocked the johnny depp to the ground, giving him a concussion, then the former frog turned ribbon turned dung beetle turned dolphin flew away into the setting sun and burned up into a beautiful display of fireworks for all of the now extinct world to not enjoy...
